# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GAB Boilerplate — Secret Schema (runtime env vars injected via SSM)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# One secret name per line. Values stored in SSM Parameter Store.
#
# DO NOT add variables that are already set in the ECS task definition
# environment (NODE_ENV, PORT, HOSTNAME) — ECS rejects duplicate names.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are baked into the client bundle at build time via
# deploy-build-args and do NOT need to be here.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# GAB API (server-only)
GAB_CLIENT_ID
GAB_SERVICE_USERNAME
GAB_SERVICE_PASSWORD

# Auth strategy (server-only, controls login modes)
AUTH_LOGIN_MODE
AUTH_ENABLE_SILENT_LOGIN

# AI (optional)
OPENAI_API_KEY
